OL,3,CFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury has
OL,4,Cprison sentence suspended
OL,6,FLeaving court, Amesbury refused to
OL,7,Fanswer questions from the waiting
OL,8,Fmedia about whether he would resign
OL,9,Fbut said: "I'd like to reiterate that
OL,10,FI sincerely apologise once again to Mr
OL,11,FFellows and his family.
OL,13,F"I'm now going to go and see my
OL,14,Ffamily, and go home, and I'll give a
OL,15,Fstatement at a later stage."
OL,17,FHonorary Recorder of Chester Judge
OL,18,FSteven Everett, sitting with two
OL,19,Fmagistrates, imposed another sentence
OL,20,Fof 10 weeks' imprisonment but
OL,21,Fsuspended it for two years.
