OL,3,CFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury has
OL,4,Cprison sentence suspended
OL,6,FHe also ordered him to carry out 200
OL,7,Fhours of unpaid work, undertake a 12-
OL,8,Fmonth alcohol monitoring requirement,
OL,9,Fgo on an anger management course and
OL,10,Fcarry out 20 days of rehabilitation
OL,11,Fwork.
OL,13,FThe Cheshire MP was caught on camera
OL,14,Fpunching a man repeatedly in the
OL,15,Fstreet in his constituency.
OL,17,FAmesbury pleaded guilty in January to
OL,18,Fassaulting Paul Fellows, 45, following
OL,19,Fa row in the street in Frodsham,
OL,20,FCheshire, in the early hours of 26
OL,21,FOctober.
