OL,6,FFootage, played again in court, showed
OL,7,FAmesbury punching Mr Fellows to the
OL,8,Fhead, knocking him to the ground, then
OL,9,Ffollowing him on to the road and
OL,10,Fstarting to punch him again, at least
OL,11,Ffive times.
OL,13,FHe was then heard saying: "You won't
OL,14,Fthreaten your MP again will you, you
OL,15,Ff****** soft lad?"
