OL,3,CFormer Labour MP Mike Amesbury has
OL,4,Cprison sentence suspended
OL,6,FIn the statement, he told police: "I
OL,7,Fthought I was about to be physically
OL,8,Fassaulted by this male. I was
OL,9,Fterrified and felt vulnerable and
OL,10,Fcornered by the male and others in the
OL,11,Fgroup."
OL,13,FHe said the man's "arms were swinging"
OL,14,Fand he thought there was no option but
OL,15,Fto "defend" himself.
OL,17,FJudge Everett said: "What he said to
OL,18,Fpolice doesn't seem to fit in with the
OL,19,FCCTV in pretty well any respect."
