OL,6,FDaniel Travers, defending, told the
OL,7,Fcourt: "He's now had three nights in
OL,8,Fprison which is an experience he will
OL,9,Fnever forget, certainly."
OL,11,FHe said the "public shaming" and
OL,12,F"embarrassment" had a huge impact on
OL,13,FAmesbury.
OL,15,FHe added: "This is a man who will
OL,16,Fcertainly rehabilitate. He will learn
OL,17,Fa very painful lesson."
